```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Load Backup-Config.xml]
    B -->|Not Found| C[Exit 1: Config Not Found]
    B -->|Found| D[Parse XML, Cache Variables]
    D --> E[Initialize Log File<br/>CP866 Encoding]
    E --> F[Test-FileIntegrity<br/>Archiver SHA256 Check]
    F -->|Mismatch| G[Exit 1: Archiver Integrity Failed]
    F -->|OK| H{Test Mode?}

    H -->|Yes| I[Invoke-TestMode]
    I --> I1[For Each Job: Check Source, Dest, Permissions]
    I1 --> I2[Send Email with Results]
    I2 --> I3{Errors?}
    I3 -->|No| I4[Exit 0]
    I3 -->|Yes| I5[Exit 1]

    H -->|No| J[Stage 1: Preparation]
    J --> J1[Log: SCRIPT START]
    J1 --> J2{Jobs Exist?}
    J2 -->|No| J3[Exit 1: No Jobs Found]
    J2 -->|Yes| K[For Each Job]

    K --> L[Invoke-Job]
    L --> L1[Log: JOB START]
    L1 --> L2{Source Exists?}
    L2 -->|No| L3[WARN: Source Not Found<br/>Error++]
    L2 -->|Yes| L4[Create Dest/RemoteDest Dirs]
    L4 --> L5[Select Mode: ArchiveAll/ByDate/Files/Folders]
    L5 --> L6[Group Files into $groups]

    L6 --> M[Invoke-Archiving]
    M --> M1[For Each Group]
    M1 --> M2[Resolve-Name<br/>Replace Placeholders]
    M2 --> M3{Archive File Exists?}
    M3 -->|Yes| M4[Add Suffix _1, _2, ...]
    M3 -->|No| M5[Create List File .txt]
    M4 --> M5

    M5 --> N[Stage 2: Main Operation]
    N --> N1[Run Archiver<br/>Start-Process]
    N1 --> N2{ExitCode = 0?}
    N2 -->|No| N3[FAIL: Archive Error<br/>Error++, Continue]
    N2 -->|Yes| O[Stage 3: Verification]

    O --> O1[Test-ArchiveIntegrity<br/>rar t / 7z t]
    O1 --> O2{Integrity OK?}
    O2 -->|No| O3[FAIL: Integrity Check<br/>Error++, Continue]
    O2 -->|Yes| P[Stage 4: Post-Operations]

    P --> P1[Copy-Remote<br/>Copy to RemoteDest]
    P1 --> Q{More Groups?}
    Q -->|Yes| M1
    Q -->|No| R[Stage 4: Local Rotation]
    R --> R1[Remove-OldFiles<br/>DaysOld + KeepCount]
    R1 --> R2[Log: JOB END]
    R2 --> S{More Jobs?}
    S -->|Yes| K
    S -->|No| T[Stage 4: Log Cleanup]

    T --> T1[Remove-OldFiles for Logs]
    T1 --> T2[Get-DiskSpaceReport]
    T2 --> U[Stage 5: Reporting]

    U --> U1[Console Summary]
    U1 --> U2[Read Log File]
    U2 --> U3{Total Errors = 0?}
    U3 -->|Yes| U4[Subject: BACKUP SUCCESS]
    U3 -->|No| U5[Subject: BACKUP ERRORS]
    U4 --> V[Send-Email]
    U5 --> V
    V --> W[Exit with Code]
    W -->|Errors = 0| X[Exit 0]
    W -->|Errors > 0| Y[Exit 1]
```

